    public class CategoryBasedRoutingPolicy
extends MapImplicitAndExplicitInputDependentPolicy<Category,java.lang.Integer>
    Defines a user-category based routing policy, according to which the output port depends on the user category. Specifically, this class is defined as a specialization of a mapping policy
